            <span class="mb-10 text-white font-sans uppercase">Contact us in the form below and we‘ll get back to you as soon as we can</span>

             <form class="form" name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true">

{#                #}{# this form doesn't work - it's just a nice boilerplate to get you up and running #}
